body.description: Kleenex tissues boxes America’s favorite tissue, Kleenex Trusted Care is the best tissue for daily use and offers soft, strong, and absorbent 2-ply care for faces and hands! Plus, you can find tissue boxes that fit your home because each tissue box is available in various colors and designs. Get the reliability and quality of Kleenex Trusted Care Facial Tissues delivered right to your door. Say goodbye to the hassle of going to the store – stock up on these trusted tissues and enjoy the convenience of having them on hand whenever you need them. Perfect for homes, offices, or any setting where soft, absorbent facial tissues are a must. Order your 4 Big Boxes today and experience the trusted care that only Kleenex can provide.

reviews.reviewText: Box issues as of late. Fall apart. Not exceptionally fond of the colors. I prefer colors that will blend in with decor...not be obnoxiously loud. Who wants kleenex boxes to stand out in a room? Dogs, cats and any animal would be better than the colors I've received in my last 3 shipments.
